caption: ⚡ In the neon-drenched alleyways of New Lumen City, cyberpunk diva Lyra Vex drops a bold, confident selfie that captures the electric pulse of the night, her skin glowing under holographic rain as she struts through the rain-soaked streets, her short, sleek dress revealing a daringly low neckline that amplifies her ample curves, all while the city hums around her in a rush of light and color palette of electric blue and magenta.💫 #cyberpunk #futurism #streetfashion #digitalart #neonaesthetics
